snippet.title: Cuphead Announcement Trailer | Xbox One | Windows 10 | Steam
snippet.description:
The all-cartoon Magical Wondergame! Cuphead will be available on September 29th for Xbox One, Windows 10 and Steam!

Pre-Order now on Xbox One and Windows 10!

http://cupheadgame.com
